oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Bethel Baptist Church
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Exterior view of the Bethel Baptist Church with two entrance doors and church bell visible. There are three people sitting on the steps of one of the entrance doors. The church and cemetery are located on the Tanner family's property.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Baptist churches; Churches; Bells
